745
00:50:13,401 --> 00:50:16,507
Everyone please stand up and
carry your child on your shoulders.

746
00:50:16,508 --> 00:50:18,599
Let's go on daddy's shoulders.

747
00:50:21,816 --> 00:50:24,208
We'll start now if everyone is ready.

748
00:50:24,209 --> 00:50:26,289
One, two...

749
