- Dan!

752
00:51:18,179 --> 00:51:19,725
Are you okay?

753
00:51:21,098 --> 00:51:23,789
You idiot, you got hurt more!

754
00:51:24,946 --> 00:51:28,396
It's okay! Let's go to the hospital!
Let's go to the hospital!

755
00:51:28,397 --> 00:51:29,833
Let's go!

