00:51:38,483 --> 00:51:41,408
Fortunately, you didn't
break a bone or anything.

757
00:51:41,409 --> 00:51:42,952
Your muscle is just in shock.

758
00:51:42,953 --> 00:51:46,695
We'll give you a shot. Just take it easy
for a few days. You'll be fine.

759
00:51:47,590 --> 00:51:50,024
Mom, are you okay?

760
00:51:50,025 --> 00:51:52,760
Yes, I'm okay.

761
00:51:58,850 --> 00:52:00,244
Cha Ki Young.

762
00:52:00,245 --> 00:52:03,272
You're not going to raise Dan
as a hidden child, right?

763
00:52:04,038 --> 00:52:06,149
Why would Dan be a hidden child?

764
00:52:06,150 --> 00:52:10,185
He becomes a hidden child if the mother
keeps hiding and running away!

765
00:52:12,459 --> 00:52:14,385
If your back is against the wall...

766
00:52:14,386 --> 00:52:16,776
Then you just have to push
your way through! That's life!

767
00:52:16,777 --> 00:52:21,066
Starting now, you do exactly as I say!
No matter what! No matter what! Got it?

768
00:52:25,782 --> 00:52:28,583
Kang Ha Ni, go home.

769
00:52:28,584 --> 00:52:30,840
Cha Ki Young is going to
be the fashion show MC.

770
00:52:30,841 --> 00:52:32,654
- Excuse me?
- Excuse me?

771
00:52:32,655 --> 00:52:34,888
Anchor Jo, are you joking right now?

772
00:52:34,889 --> 00:52:37,668
Don't mess with me,
I'm not playing right now.

773
00:52:37,669 --> 00:52:40,747
I refuse to obey your order.
It's unfair, Sir.

774
00:52:40,748 --> 00:52:44,075
