you're no longer an anchor!

775
00:52:44,076 --> 00:52:46,501
I'll post the personnel
appointment tomorrow morning.

776
00:52:47,222 --> 00:52:49,727
I refuse to be the MC as well!

777
00:52:49,728 --> 00:52:51,821
Then turn in your resignation tomorrow!

778
00:52:53,748 --> 00:52:55,681
