the show when I look this?

779
00:52:55,682 --> 00:52:57,305
We have less than 30 minutes
before the show starts!

780
00:52:57,306 --> 00:52:59,899
You kept on reporting the news
while you were in labor, remember?

781
00:53:00,553 --> 00:53:02,520
Your dress is all ripped, right?

782
00:53:02,521 --> 00:53:06,580
Kang Ha Ni, take off your dress and give it
to Cha Ki Young when you go home. Quickly!

783
00:53:26,677 --> 00:53:29,764
Mom, you look pretty.

