00:53:31,902 --> 00:53:34,066
The little rascal knows
his mommy is pretty.

785
00:53:34,695 --> 00:53:40,288
I'll take good care of Dan,
so go and show them what you got.

786
00:53:41,194 --> 00:53:45,153
- Dan, have a good time with Mr. Jo, okay?
- Mom, fighting!

787
00:53:45,154 --> 00:53:46,809
Fighting!

788
00:53:46,810 --> 00:53:48,160
Fighting!

789
00:53:51,575 --> 00:53:52,881
Hey, Mom.

790
00:53:52,882 --> 00:53:55,318
- When did you get here?
- A little while ago.

791
00:54:00,942 --> 00:54:02,871
Hello, Ma'am.

792
00:54:10,278 --> 00:54:12,532
Eun Cha, I brought what you asked for.

793
00:54:12,533 --> 00:54:14,337
But, why did you call me?

794
00:54:14,338 --> 00:54:15,967
Dong Shik.

795
00:54:15,968 --> 00:54:18,975
Starting now, I'm going to gamble.

796
00:54:18,976 --> 00:54:21,787
And I need you to keep record of it.

797
00:54:21,788 --> 00:54:24,230
Gamble? What kind of gamble?

798
00:54:25,102 --> 00:54:27,274
I told you raise your arms.

799
00:54:28,293 --> 00:54:30,616
If I let Cha Ki Young
host the fashion show...

800
00:54:30,617 --> 00:54:32,846
I might not get nominated.

801
00:54:32,847 --> 00:54:36,229
But I'm still going to do it.
Do you know why?

802
00:54:37,002 --> 00:54:39,208
Because even if Kim Pal Soon
gets nominated...

803
00:54:39,209 --> 00:54:42,993
My macho image right now
won't get me elected.

804
00:54:45,372 --> 00:54:46,789
And?

805
00:54:48,144 --> 00:54:50,433
As Dan's surrogate father...

806
00:54:50,988 --> 00:54:52,953
What's connected to it?

807
00:54:55,425 --> 00:55:01,370
A single mother like Cha Ki Young and
women like her are powerless in society.

808
00:55:01,371 --> 00:55:03,400
What do we call something like this?

809
00:55:06,100 --> 00:55:07,520
Feminists?

810
00:55:07,521 --> 00:55:14,331
As of now, I'm going to become the
leading feminist in the Republic of Korea!

811
00:55:17,589 --> 00:55:19,719
Me too, me too, me too.

812
00:55:33,349 --> 00:55:36,359
Hello, my name is Cha Ki Young.

813
00:55:36,360 --> 00:55:38,318
Just a moment!

814
00:56:04,985 --> 00:56:09,246
Now, we have two MCs today.

815
00:56:10,030 --> 00:56:13,640
Announcer Cha Ki Young and her son Cha Dan!

816
00:56:13,641 --> 00:56:16,052
Please give them a round of applause!

817
00:56:22,662 --> 00:56:25,911
Designer Oh Shin Hee's
fashion show concept for today...

818
00:56:25,912 --> 00:56:29,134
is a happy life for the working women.

