00:56:29,135 --> 00:56:33,599
And we can't leave out children
in that happy life now, can we?

820
00:56:33,600 --> 00:56:38,130
But you try to work and
your child cries out for you.

821
00:56:38,131 --> 00:56:40,875
So you take care of your child but
then your job cries out for you.

822
00:56:41,434 --> 00:56:42,702
Today...

823
00:56:42,703 --> 00:56:45,363
this fashion show is
a place to cheer and support

824
00:56:45,364 --> 00:56:48,498
the weary lives of those career women.

825
00:56:49,802 --> 00:56:54,927
Now, please bring a chair
for our little Chan. Quickly.

