00:56:59,199 --> 00:57:01,663
You brought out a pretty red chair for him.

827
00:57:03,356 --> 00:57:05,888
Dan will be hosting next to his mother...

828
00:57:06,413 --> 00:57:11,499
and Designer Oh Shin Hee will
personally set him down in this chair!

829
00:57:11,500 --> 00:57:14,285
Ma'am, please come out.

830
00:57:24,274 --> 00:57:26,035
Thank you.

831
00:57:26,036 --> 00:57:27,635
Okay then...

832
00:57:28,136 --> 00:57:31,807
I will hand over the mic to
Announcer Cha Ki Young now.

833
00:57:45,085 --> 00:57:47,482
The Seoul Designer Association has died

834
00:57:47,483 --> 00:57:49,370
and Channel Korea is
giving its full support.

835
00:57:49,371 --> 00:57:52,672
Oh Shin Hee's fashion show will now start!

836
00:58:18,921 --> 00:58:21,235
Pedro, why are you...

837
00:58:23,184 --> 00:58:25,746
Unbelievable. I took a picture of him.

838
00:58:35,684 --> 00:58:37,370
- Why are you...
- Hey, hey...

839
00:58:37,371 --> 00:58:40,578
Mother, do you need something?

840
00:58:40,579 --> 00:58:42,544
No.

841
00:59:13,549 --> 00:59:15,668
<i>Announcer Cha Ki Young who publicly
claimed to be a single mother</i>

842
00:59:15,669 --> 00:59:19,093
